    <h2 class="terminal-list__title">Black Tea</h2>
    <p class="terminal-list__description"> 
      Black Tea is fully-oxidized, resulting in a strong robust flavor. Though originally created in China, 
      black teas are now cultivated worldwide, giving you many sources to choose from. Black tea retains its 
      flavor for several years and therefore has longer shelf life. Be careful when you choose where to get your 
      tea from because machine-processed black teas have lower quality. For quality and making in bulk, 
      we suggest you choose loose leaves black teas from a trusted source. 
    </p>

